contrary to what you may think, this file is for people who are developing this further.

HOW TO FIX INCREMENTAL CHANGES

change the gradle settings from gradle to IJ, run the project, change it back

HOW TO SAVE GUI CHANGES

this is the most annoying.
Make your changes
Changeg the settings in gui designer to "binary"
do the "HOW TO FIX INCREMENTAL CHANGES FIX"
run with gradle
Take a sanity break